ygData.messageBody:
Beld,

You posted a question on the Soerbaird Fellowship BB about the Aquaducts on
the 17th, and I have posted a reply.
There is a map at EQ'Lizer for the Qeynos Aquaducts. The most detailed map I
have seen to date. The Bank entry it lists as an exit only now.

So you don't need to go to that BB to get the info, the link to the map is
below.

http://www.gameznet.com/eq/maps/qey_aqua.gif


--
Cronik Khaos <Dark Omen>
16th Season TSK
